有證據顯示石炭獸類，作為河馬的親屬<ref name="Cetartiodactyla">{{cite journal en|last= Boisserie|first= Jean-Renaud|coauthors= Fabrice Lihoreau and Michel Brunet|title= The position of Hippopotamidae within Cetartiodactyla|journal= Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|volume= 102|issue= 5|pages= 1537-1541|url= http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/102/5/1537|accessdate= 2007-06-09|date= February 2005|archive-date= 2018-11-20|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181120203413/http://www.pnas.org/content/102/5/1537.full|dead-url= no}}</ref>，有可能是[[鯨魚|鯨魚]]祖先的近親。<ref name="DNA">{{Cite journal en | url = http://mbe.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/14/5/537 | title = More DNA support for a Cetacea/Hippopotamidae clade: the blood-clotting protein gene gamma-fibrinogen | author = Gatesy, J. | journal = Molecular Biology and Evolution | volume = 14 | pages = 537-543 | access-date = 2008-04-09 | archive-date = 2010-05-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100505025758/http://mbe.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/14/5/537 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Genomes">{{Cite journal en | title = Analyses of mitochondrial genomes strongly support a hippopotamus-whale clade | volume = 265 | issue = 1412 | year = 1998 | pages = 2251 | journal = Proceedings of the Royal Society | author = Ursing, B.M. | coauthor = U. Arnason}}</ref>但是，最早的石炭獸科只是於始新世中期出現，是[[古鯨小目|古鯨小目]]在完全進入水中生活的時期之後。

